189
00:19:40,439 --> 00:19:43,454
- I'm trying to help.
- Get back! Why?

190
00:19:44,377 --> 00:19:47,214
Because I didn't know who I 
was working for then, but I do now.

191
00:19:47,824 --> 00:19:50,284
